title: Romania captain cited for dangerous tackle vs Canada at RWC
text: Romania captain cited for dangerous tackle vs Canada at RWC Thursday, 8 October 2015 (7 minutes ago) LONDON (AP) " Romania captain Mihai Macovei has been cited for a dangerous tackle in the 17-15 win against Canada in the Rugby World Cup.Macovei's two tries and driving runs from the back of the scrum helped Romania overturn a 15-0...
